Package poker

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EvaluateCardHand
    The EvaluateCardHand Interface implemented by classes to evaluate Card Hands.
    EvaluatePokerHand
    The EvaluatePokerHand Interface implemented by classes to evaluate Poker Card Hands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    The Card class is used to hold a Suit and CardValue for each card.
    Dealer
    The Dealer class is used to act as a dealer for the Table.
    Deck
    The Deck class holds a brand new deck of 52 cards.
    FiveCardPokerDealer
    The FiveCardPokerDealer class is an extension of the Dealer class and is used to act as a poker dealer for the Table.
    FiveCardPokerEvalEngine
    The FiveCardPokerEvalEngine class is used to evaluate and sort Poker Hands.
    Hand
    The Hand class is used to hold Cards and the Hand's value when it is evaluated and the Result of the evaluation.
    Player
    The Player class is used to hold a card Hand.
    Table
    The Table class is used to hold Players.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CardValue
    Enum class used to create ordinal and integer values for Cards
    PokerHandValue
    Enum class used to create ordinal and integer value hands for Poker evaluations.
    Result
    Enum class used to create ordinal and integer value results for Poker Hand evaluations.
    Suit
    Enum class used to create ordinal value card suits.
